16
00:02:16,061 --> 00:02:20,157
<i>He'd probably feel a lot like I did when I learned I wasn't human.</i>

17
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:37,012
<i>You don't know who you are...</i>

18
00:02:37,182 --> 00:02:38,844
