21
00:03:07,613 --> 00:03:09,514
- Who's that? - It's a monster!

22
00:03:09,682 --> 00:03:12,846
- I'm out of here. - Let's get out of here. Run!

23
00:03:16,321 --> 00:03:18,790
This no am home.

24
00:03:18,957 --> 00:03:22,485
<i>After all this time, Metropolis still knows so little about...</i>

25
00:03:22,661 --> 00:03:23,661
<i>the real Superman.</i>

26
00:03:23,829 --> 00:03:26,492
<i>Only one person is known to have pierced the iron wall...</i>

27
00:03:26,665 --> 00:03:28,657
<i>around the Man of Steel:</i>

28
00:03:28,834 --> 00:03:31,394
<i>Professor Emil Hamilton of S.T.A.R. Labs.</i>

29
00:03:31,570 --> 00:03:35,302
<i>Rumor has it that he's even been to Superman's secret hideaway...</i>

30
00:03:35,474 --> 00:03:38,911
<i>a mysterious fortress hidden somewhere near the North Pole.</i>

31
00:03:39,078 --> 00:03:41,843
<i>I tried asking Hamilton if this was Superman's home...</i>

32
00:03:42,014 --> 00:03:44,074
<i>but the professor declined to comment.</i>

33
00:03:44,249 --> 00:03:48,152
North Pole? Home?

34
00:04:35,033 --> 00:04:37,195
Why am you locked up?

35
00:04:37,636 --> 00:04:40,538
Me bet you do nothing wrong.

36
00:04:59,324 --> 00:05:03,659
Doggie, you am new friend?

37
00:05:39,264 --> 00:05:40,823
<i>Welcome to Krypton.</i>

38
00:05:42,935 --> 00:05:44,767
<i>What is it you wish to know?</i>

39
00:05:44,937 --> 00:05:47,236
Who am me?

40
00:05:47,406 --> 00:05:50,103
Where am home?

41
00:05:50,275 --> 00:05:52,301
<i>One moment, please.</i>

42
00:05:55,647 --> 00:05:58,648
<i>This is your home... the planet Krypton.</i>

43
00:05:58,817 --> 00:06:02,948
<i>A majestic world of scientific achievement and prosperity.</i>

44
00:06:07,392 --> 00:06:10,328
<i>You are Kal-El, son of Jor-El.</i>

45
00:06:15,701 --> 00:06:18,102
<i>Your father was a world-renowned scientist...</i>

46
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:21,263
<i>and member of Krypton's ruling council.</i>

47
00:06:22,975 --> 00:06:26,969
<i>An only child, you were born shortly before the end...</i>

48
00:06:27,145 --> 00:06:30,013
<i>of Krypton's seventh age.</i>

49
00:06:43,896 --> 00:06:48,163
Who let you out? Don't tell me we've had visitors.

50
00:07:16,695 --> 00:07:18,687
Oh, no.

51
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:38,567
Me make Krypton.

52
00:08:42,447 --> 00:08:46,714
Then me am home.

53
00:09:21,535 --> 00:09:23,299
Too many chairs.

54
00:09:23,471 --> 00:09:26,031
Me make room.

55
00:09:26,874 --> 00:09:28,934
He's up there!

56
00:09:29,543 --> 00:09:31,842
He's wrecking everything in sight.

57
00:09:34,949 --> 00:09:36,713
Dada?

58
00:09:44,725 --> 00:09:49,823
Dada. No be scared, me am Kay-Lil.

59
00:09:49,997 --> 00:09:52,899
Me take you home.

60
00:09:56,637 --> 00:10:00,233
That's just dandy. Now we got a hostage situation.

61
00:10:00,408 --> 00:10:02,502
I want this area locked down.

62
00:10:02,877 --> 00:10:05,506
Get those people out of there.

63
00:10:11,185 --> 00:10:13,177
Scram, Lane. This is a police matter.

64
00:10:13,354 --> 00:10:16,449
Yeah, Turpin. Like that really works with me.

65
00:10:16,624 --> 00:10:18,092
Loiz?

66
00:10:22,530 --> 00:10:24,999
- Bizarro? - You know this guy?

67
00:10:25,166 --> 00:10:27,533
Figures, all the wackos come to you.

68
00:10:30,171 --> 00:10:32,902
Me show Loiz new home?

69
00:10:33,074 --> 00:10:36,511
Hold it, bub. You're not showing anyone any...

70
00:10:38,579 --> 00:10:40,411
- Hey! - Wait.

71
00:10:40,581 --> 00:10:42,607
I'll go. I'd love to.

72
00:10:43,484 --> 00:10:45,783
I can't let you do that. It's too dangerous.

73
00:10:45,953 --> 00:10:47,615
And duking it out with him is safe?

74
00:10:47,788 --> 00:10:50,724
Superman will be here soon. I'll keep him calm in the meantime.

75
00:10:51,025 --> 00:10:52,960
Okay, let's go.

76
00:11:04,572 --> 00:11:07,235
Oh, great. Now we got two hostages.

77
00:11:15,149 --> 00:11:18,244
This my house. What you think?

78
00:11:22,256 --> 00:11:23,884
It's you.

79
00:11:30,998 --> 00:11:34,491
Hey, you scare Krypto.

80
00:11:37,538 --> 00:11:40,372
But me forgive you.

81
00:11:42,977 --> 00:11:45,310
Let me guess. Bizarro?

82
00:11:47,848 --> 00:11:50,647
- Any idea what he's doing? - Remodeling.

83
00:11:50,818 --> 00:11:52,980
He thinks he's me, so he's trying to create...

84
00:11:53,154 --> 00:11:55,487
- his own version of Krypton. - Naturally.

85
00:12:05,733 --> 00:12:07,326
That building won't last long.

86
00:12:07,501 --> 00:12:08,560
I'll be right back.

87
00:12:08,736 --> 00:12:11,831
If Krypton is what Bizarro wants, that's what he's gonna get.

88
00:12:12,006 --> 00:12:15,170
I had to take this beat. Humans weren't nuts enough.

89
00:12:17,211 --> 00:12:20,773
- Loiz sit? - SUre.

90
00:12:33,861 --> 00:12:39,198
