91
00:12:39,366 --> 00:12:41,961
Krypton? You remember Krypton?

92
00:12:42,436 --> 00:12:44,405
Shiny ball show me.

93
00:12:44,572 --> 00:12:49,010
It say me am Kay-Lil, and it show me baby me.

94
00:12:49,276 --> 00:12:52,940
