104
00:13:58,045 --> 00:14:02,915
Superman play with Krypto. Here, fetch!

105
00:14:03,183 --> 00:14:04,481
No!

106
00:14:13,927 --> 00:14:15,657
Superman!

107
00:14:31,578 --> 00:14:33,171
