108
00:14:33,347 --> 00:14:38,479
Superman, Krypto, Dada, Loiz, all here with me.

109
00:14:40,254 --> 00:14:42,485
Krypton pretty.

110
00:14:42,656 --> 00:14:44,648
So sad now it have to blow up.

111
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:48,422
Wait.

112
00:15:07,214 --> 00:15:09,080
